      <a href="https://npm.runkit.com/wink-nlp-utils">break paragraphs into sentences</a>,
      <a href="https://npm.runkit.com/wink-tokenizer">tokenize</a> them,
      <a href="https://npm.runkit.com/wink-pos-tagger">POS tag</a>
